### ===== DONOR ENDPOINTS =====

### Get all donors
GET http://localhost:9999/donors

### Get specific donor by ID
GET http://localhost:9999/donors/770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001

### Create new donor
POST http://localhost:9999/donors
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "first_name": "John",
    "last_name": "Doe",
    "phone": "+1234567890",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

### Update donor
PUT http://localhost:9999/donors/770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "first_name": "John",
    "last_name": "Doe",
    "phone": "+1987654321",
    "email": "john.updated@example.com",
    "is_verified": true
}

### ===== DONATION ENDPOINTS =====

### Get all donations
GET http://localhost:9999/donations

### Get donations by campaign ID
GET http://localhost:9999/donations?campaign_id=770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001

### Get specific donation by ID
GET http://localhost:9999/donations/880e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001

### Create new donation
POST http://localhost:9999/donations
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "campaign_id": "770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001",
    "amount": 100.50,
    "donor_id": "770e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001",
    "message": "Good luck with the campaign!",
    "is_anonymous": false,
    "payment_method": "MercadoPago",
    "status": "completed"
}

### Update donation status
PUT http://localhost:9999/donations/880e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "completed"
}